                <h3 class="font-bold">{label}</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-base-content/80">这里可以补充对应类别的项目说明、链接或截图。</p>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </section> -->

    <section class="py-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
        <Icon name="lucide:git-pull-request" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
        <span>协作经历待补充</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="card bg-base-200 p-6">
        <ul class="space-y-5">
          {
            [
              {
                project: "协作方向 1 待补充",
                description: "这里可以写你参与过的协作、贡献或团队项目。",
              },
              {
                project: "协作方向 2 待补充",
                description: "这里可以写你在项目中的角色、负责模块和产出。",
              },
              {
                project: "协作方向 3 待补充",
                description: "如果暂时没有协作经历，也可以先留作占位。",
              },
            ].map((contrib) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-base-300 p-2 rounded-full">
                  <Icon name="lucide:git-commit" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">{contrib.project}</h3>
                  <p class="text-base-content/80">{contrib.description}</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            ))
          }
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </MainCard>
</BaseLayout>
